lambda.name: makeRepairRoutingPayloads
reindexState
incrementSimSteps
lambda.code:
const { state } = input
    const incr = x => {x.steps = x.steps + 1}
    incr( state.sim )
    state.cities.forEach( incr )
    state.producers.forEach( incr )
    state.hubs.forEach( incr )
    return state

lambda.name: transferResources
manufactureProducts
makeTransitOrderFromPayloadAndRoute
lambda.code:
const { payload, waypoints } = input 
const { canRepair, vehicle, sim } = payload 

const status = (waypoints.length>0 && canRepair) ? "Repair" : "Cancelled"

return {
    id: `${vehicle}/${waypoints.map( x=> x.id).join('-')}#${new Date().valueOf()}`,
    vehicle,
    sim,
    waypoints: status === "Repair" ? waypoints : [],
    steps: 0,
    visited: [],
    status: { id: status }
}
